<!-- What do we do for you? -->
<section class="container text-center home-section" id="instructions">
  <h2>What does BrexitHedge do for me?</h2>
  <p>BrexitHedge helps EU citizens living in the UK protect their residency right to stay post Brexit.<br>BrexitHedge provide a unique infrastructure of authenticity and trust, and give people the ability to unlock data.<br>BrexitHedge servers are based in Norway.</p>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <div class="flexbox-vertical feature">
      <%= image_tag('vault', class: "feature-image-vault") %>
      <h4>Collect and Save</h4>
      <p class="text-justify">We help you to collect your proof of residency. We also securely save them to keep your personal data confidential. <strong>We never distribute or sell your data to anyone.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <div class="flexbox-vertical feature">
      <i class="fa fa-unlock-alt feature-image-unlock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      <h4>Unlock</h4>
      <p class="text-justify">We offer a unique and secure unlocking process of your data and send it <strong>only to who you designated. We can send your data to the Home Office on request.</strong> </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <div class="flexbox-vertical feature">
      <%= image_tag('proof', class: "feature-image-proof") %>
      <h4>Prove</h4>
      <p class="text-justify">We ensure the authenticity of data thanks to blockchain technology. We also use <strong>UK Guardians to confirm your information.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Feedback -->
<section class="home-section" id="feedback" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,128,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,36,51,0.4) 50%), url(<%= image_path('banner2.jpg') %>);">
  <div class="container text-center" id="reviews">
    <h2>Act now!</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="review-box">
          <p>“I did not have any family in the UK when my parents passed away. I was devastated by the news and completely lost. I stayed more than 20 weeks alone under British Authorities control before being allowed to join my grand-parents in Poland. My parents had not named guardians as it is something you are never asked.“</p>
          <p>Imre</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="review-box">
          <p>“When my sister had a deadly accident, she was divorced from her husband with two sons and living in the UK. My nephews have been placed in an orphanage as there was no named guardian and UK authorithies judge their father was not eligible. I finally got custody after four months and a long and painful process for them. I have myself named guardians. It should be as natural as it is for an insurance policy.“</p>
          <p>Iva</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

